uble with last gasp strikes\" />\n*[[Johan Cruijff Shield]]: [[Johan Cruijff-schaal VII|2001\u201302]]<ref name=\"jcs\">{{cite web|title=Seizoen 2002/2003 Johan Cruijff Schaal : Ajax \u2013 PSV (3\u20131)|url=http://www.supver-psv.nl/cgi-bin/algemeen/wedstrijd.pl?nummer=73|publisher=supver-psv.nl|accessdate=20 August 2014}}</ref>\n\n'''International'''\n*[[Africa Cup of Nations]]: [[2006 Africa Cup of Nations|2006]]<ref name=\"Mido\" /><ref name=\"Mido thrown out of Egyptian squad\" />\n\n'''Individual'''\n*[[Belgian Ebony Shoe]]: [[Belgian Ebony Shoe#Winners|2001]]<ref name=\"Portrait of a young pro\" />\n*Belgian League Young Player of the Year: 2000\u201301<ref name=\"Portrait of a young pro\" />\n*Egyptian Young Footballer of the Year: 2000\u201301<ref name=\"Portrait of a young pro\" />\n*[[CAF Awards#African Young Player of the Year|African Young Player of the Year]]: 2001\u201302<ref name=\"Portrait of a young pro\" />\n\n===As a manager===\n'''Zamalek'''\n*[[Egypt Cup]]: [[2014 Egypt Cup|2014]]<ref name=\"egcup14\" />\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|30em}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Mido (footballer)}}\n*{{FIFA player|183023|Mido}}\n*{{Soccerbase}}\n\n{{Navboxes colour\n|title=Egypt squads\n| bg        = #DD0000\n| fg        = white\n| bordercolor = black\n|list1=\n{{Egypt squad 2002 African Cup of Nations}}\n{{Egypt squad 2004 African Cup of Nations}}\n{{Egypt squad 2006 Africa Cup of Nations}}\n}}\n{{Navboxes colour\n|bg=gold\n|fg=navy\n|title= Awards\n|list1=\n{{CAF Most Promising Talent of the Year}}\n{{Ebony Shoe}}\n}}\n{{Zamalek SC managers}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{Good article}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mido}}\n[[Category:1983 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Egyptian Muslims]]\n[[Category:Sportspeople from Cairo]]\n[[Category:Egyptian footballers]]\n[[Category:Association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Zamalek SC players]]\n[[Category:K.A.A. Gent players]]\n[[Category:AFC Ajax players]]\n[[Category:RC Celta de Vigo players]]