ccessdate=4 January 2016}}</ref>\n\n{| class=wikitable style=\"text-align: center\"\n|+ Managerial record by team and tenure\n|-\n!rowspan=2|Team\n!rowspan=2|From\n!rowspan=2|To\n!colspan=5|Record\n|-\n!{{abbr|P|Matches played}}!!{{abbr|W|Matches won}}!!{{abbr|D|Matches drawn}}!!{{abbr|L|Matches lost}}!!{{abbr|Win %|Win percentage}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]]\n|align=left|21 January 2014\n|align=left|29 July 2014\n{{WDL|31|16|8|7}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Ismaily]]<ref>http://www.filgoal.com/arabic/news.aspx?NewsID=180532</ref>\n|align=left|15 July 2015\n|align=left|20 December 2015\n{{WDL|9|5|1|3}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Zamalek SC|Zamalek]]\n|align=left|4 January 2016 \n|align=left|9 February 2016 \n{{WDL|7|4|1|2}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Wadi Degla]]\n|align=left|8 November 2016\n|align=left|3 December 2017\n{{WDL|42|10|14|18}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Al-Wehda Club (Mecca)|Al Wehda]]\n|align=left|17 December 2018\n|align=left|19 March 2019\n{{WDL|13|6|3|4}}\n|-\n|align=left|[[Misr Lel Makkasa SC|El Makkasa]]\n|align=left|9 June 2019\n|align=left|21 January 2020\n{{WDL|17|3|5|9}}\n|-\n!colspan=3|Total\n{{WDLtot|119|44|32|43}}\n|}\n\n==Honours==\n\n===As a player===\n'''Zamalek'''\n*[[African Cup Winners' Cup]]: [[2000 African Cup Winners' Cup|2000]]<ref>{{cite web|title=African Cup Winners' Cup 2000|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.coupe.zamalek.canon-de-yaounde.155352.en.html|publisher=footballdatabase.eu|accessdate=2 August 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=African Cup Winners' Cup 2000|url=http://www.footballdatabase.eu/football.coupe.canon-de-yaounde.zamalek.155353.en.html|publisher=footballdatabase.eu|accessdate=20 August 2014}}</ref>\n\n'''Ajax'''\n*[[Eredivisie]]: [[2001\u201302 Eredivisie|2001\u201302]], [[2010\u201311 Eredivisie|2010\u201311]]<ref name=\"Mido\" /><ref name=\"Ajax seal double with last gasp strikes\" />\n*[[KNVB Cup]]: [[2001\u201302 KNVB Cup|2001\u201302]]<ref name=\"Ajax seal double with last gasp strikes\" />\n*[[Johan Cruijff Shie